data.description: Sprawling ranch with walk out basement. This home is so well cared for and ready for some new owners. Step into your new home and you will be greeting by amazing views out the living room windows. Large living room lets you relax with the fireplace on a views of pikes peak. Open floor plan allows for great entertaining with a gourmet kitchen overlooking the living room and breakfast nook. Beautiful counters with lots of space as well as cabinets for storage. Gas range in the island with hood vent. Enjoy the beautiful evening watching the sunset on the deck or enjoy the views of Pikes Peak. Split bedroom design with an amazing primary suite that offers a large bedroom, bath and superb closet space. 2 more bedrooms and bath on main level. Basement is a great entertaining area that offers 2 more bedrooms and a office or a 3rd bedroom. Large family room with wet bar, wine cage and a walk out to your back yard. Don't forget the movie theater room with large screen and projector that stay. Home backs up to open space, so no views will be obstructed. Large pergola with fire pit in back as well as a detached 2 car garage. 16 foot gate for RV, Boat or any of your parking needs. This home has so much to offer, you do not want to miss this home.
